# vim-clipboardwatcher

clipboard watcher

## Usage

start watch clipboard changes
```
let watcher = clipboardwatcher#watch({x,y->execute('echo y',0)})
```

stop the watching.
```
call watcher.stop()
```

## Requirements

golang

## Installation

```
cd clipboardwatcher && go get -d && go build
```

